# 💻 Software Requirements

The following software tools and environments are necessary to develop, flash, and monitor the **Eye-Pulse** system:

| Software | Specification | Purpose |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Operating System** | Windows 10/11, macOS, or Linux | Primary development environment for coding and flashing |
| **Arduino IDE** | Version 2.0 or higher | Main platform for writing and uploading Embedded C firmware |
| **VS Code** | With Python Extension | Used for running the Streamlit-based IoT dashboard |
| **Python** | Version 3.9 or higher | Backend language for processing and visualizing real-time data |
| **Blynk IoT App** | Android or iOS | Mobile interface for remote monitoring and risk alerts |
| **Web Browser** | Chrome, Edge, or Firefox | To access the cloud-based IoT dashboard and patient records |

> **Note:** Ensure all Python dependencies (Streamlit, Pandas, Plotly) are installed via pip before launching the dashboard application.
